WEBVTT

00:00:06.878 --> 00:00:09.839
Ertaga do’stingizning tug’ilgan
kuni, va u...

00:00:09.839 --> 00:00:12.091
yaqinda... muammo esa
buni unutganligingizda.

00:00:12.383 --> 00:00:15.428
U 1 yoshdan katta,
ammo umriboqiydek ko’rinadi.

00:00:15.428 --> 00:00:18.306
Siz ishonishingiz mumkin bo’lgan yosh
2 va 200 orasida.

00:00:18.473 --> 00:00:20.683
tug’ilgan kuni bo’layotgan do’stingiz
- gigant,

00:00:20.683 --> 00:00:23.811
va siz bu haqida unutganingizni
kimdir bilib qoladigan bo’lsa,

00:00:23.811 --> 00:00:25.521
siz bazmning bir qismiga aylanasiz.

00:00:25.772 --> 00:00:29.650
Novvoy puxtalik bilan tog’dek 
keladigan tort tayyorladi

00:00:29.901 --> 00:00:35.031
va sizning vazifangiz gigantning yoshini
tort markazida shokolad bilan tasvirlash